Nathalie Richard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathalie_Richard 0 Nathalie Richard (born 6 January 1963) is a French actress. Richard was born in Paris, France. She received the Prix Michel Simon film prize for most promising actress/actor for her role in the 1988 Jacques Rivette film Gang of Four.
